<p><a href="powser.html">Power serious: Haskell magic</a>
</p><pre>revert (0:ft) = rs where rs = 0 : 1/(ft#rs)</pre>
<a href="tinysort.html">Tiniest C sort function?</a>
<pre>s(a,n)int*a;{n-->1?s(a,n),s(a+1,n),n=*a,*a=a[1],a[n>*a]=n:0;}</pre>
